## Instead of using Streamlit's default components, we'll use:
st.columns() for product grids.
st.container(border=True) for clean product cards.
Custom CSS (style.css) to give the app a modern look.
Session state to manage search results and the selected product.

This will make the app look much closer to a real shopping website while still keeping development fast for your one-week deadline.

